<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空站在观音菩萨面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把寺院里发生的一切都告诉了观音菩萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只叫黑风王的黑熊精偷走了袈裟。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空继续说，“我要求他把袈裟还回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们打了一架，但那黑熊精说他要去吃午饭，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后就躲在洞里不出来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我踢门，叫骂了一个多小时了，但他就是不出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你必须帮帮我。”观音菩萨叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唐僧不应该把那袈裟给和尚看的。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“袈裟是佛祖的宝贝。其他人看到了，自然会想要。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当住持想要得到袈裟时，就很可能会伤害唐僧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我同意。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我告诉过唐僧很多次不要做傻事，但他还是......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你应该把火扑灭的。”观音菩萨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的话打断了悟空：“你做的太不好了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看着地面。他抬脚踢了一下地上的小石头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道。”他咕哝着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会帮你拿回袈裟的。”观音菩萨说，“我们走吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和观音菩萨飞过了大海。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他们就落在了山上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那黑风王的岩洞在哪里？”观音菩萨问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就在附近。”悟空说，“我们悄悄地过去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们听到一阵脚步声朝自己走了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和观音菩萨躲了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个道士沿着小路走了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那道士拿着一个盘子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>盘子里有一个闪闪发光的紫色药丸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>道士自言自语。“今天真不错。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“黑风王得到了一件新袈裟，那可是佛祖的宝贝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我希望他喜欢我给他制的这药丸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这会让他长生不老的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空用他的火眼金睛盯了那道士一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那不是道士。”悟空意识到，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是只狼精打扮成的道士。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空的眼睛一亮。“我有主意了，观音菩萨！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一小会儿，那道士站在了黑风王的洞穴面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他敲了敲门，洞门打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么还在这儿，小猴儿？”黑风王喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他看到那道士时，他笑了：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦， 是你啊，我的老朋友！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>抱歉对你大吼大叫了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有只讨厌的猴精刚才在这里待了一会儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看四周：“我想他是走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里有只猴精？”道士问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”黑熊说，“他一直在敲我的门，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>对我大喊大叫。他太无礼了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑风王拍了拍道士的肩膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们现在不谈他了。很高兴见到你。你最近怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很好。”道士说，“我给你带了个礼物，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>庆祝你新得到的佛祖宝贝。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他举起了那个装着药丸的盘子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑风王看上去很感兴趣：“这是什么药丸？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这药丸十分特别。”道士微笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我专门为你制作的。它可以让你长生不老。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑风王摸着自己的下巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊。我今天早上还在想，我要长生不老。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑熊精拿起药丸，嘴巴张得大大的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他刚要把药丸放进嘴里，那药丸动了动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯？这药丸刚刚......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑风王的话还没说完，那药丸就从他手里跳了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>药丸冲进了黑熊精的嘴里，顺着他的喉咙滚了下去。咕咚！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>